    <item>
      <title>How to Overcome the Ego and Find Joy in Life?</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/wiaposts/overcome-ego-and-find-joy-in-life/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/wiaposts/overcome-ego-and-find-joy-in-life/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;../../assets/images/wiapost/5290-overcome-ego-and-find-joy-in-life.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Ego and Joy of Life&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Ego and Joy of Life 
    &lt;div id=&#34;ego-and-joy-of-life&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#ego-and-joy-of-life&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you think, &lt;em&gt;&amp;ldquo;The ego within us &lt;br&gt;
wants to do something difficult because, &lt;br&gt;
against the difficult, one feels, &lt;br&gt;
&amp;lsquo;I am someone, doing such a difficult thing,&amp;rsquo;&amp;rdquo;&lt;/em&gt; &lt;br&gt;
then think again.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It is not about seeking difficulty. &lt;br&gt;
If you challenge someone by asking, &lt;br&gt;
&lt;em&gt;&amp;ldquo;Why are you doing X in the most difficult way?&amp;rdquo;&lt;/em&gt; &lt;br&gt;
they will likely respond, &lt;br&gt;
&lt;em&gt;&amp;ldquo;This is the easiest and simplest way.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>The Power Within</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/wiaposts/the-power-within/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 08:33:00 +0530</pubDate>
      <author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/wiaposts/the-power-within/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;../../assets/images/wiapost/5254-The-Power-Within.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;The Power Within 
    &lt;div id=&#34;the-power-within&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#the-power-within&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We all have the power to heal our own soul,&lt;br&gt;
Yet many still suffer, not feeling whole.&lt;br&gt;
Some can heal others, it’s their choice to make,&lt;br&gt;
To mend what is broken or let it ache.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A rare few taste the sweetness of freedom&amp;rsquo;s embrace,&lt;br&gt;
They rise above suffering, in every case.&lt;br&gt;
It’s not that the world spares them from pain,&lt;br&gt;
But they choose their freedom, again and again.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Ways to Experience the Bliss</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/wiaposts/Ways-to-Experience-the-Bliss/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Sep 2023 08:33:00 +0530</pubDate>
      <author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/wiaposts/Ways-to-Experience-the-Bliss/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;../../assets/images/wiapost/5235-Ways-to-Experience-the-Bliss.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Ways to Experience the Bliss&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Ways to Experience the Bliss 
    &lt;div id=&#34;ways-to-experience-the-bliss&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#ways-to-experience-the-bliss&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Humans are searching for peace and want to experience bliss. &lt;br&gt;
Humans want to get it by searching. &lt;br&gt;
First he search for knowledge then he search for work &lt;br&gt;
After that he search for money then search for  &lt;br&gt;
network, relationship and power.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When you find a moment to reflect on your actions and accomplishments, &lt;br&gt;
take the time to sit and ponder. &lt;br&gt;
Are those with wealth the ones who find peace and experience bliss? &lt;br&gt;
Do those with power, networks, and resources find peace and experience bliss? &lt;br&gt;
Are the &amp;lsquo;smart&amp;rsquo; individuals, adept at managing business, relationships, &lt;br&gt;
and earning a livelihood, the ones who experience bliss and peace? &lt;br&gt;
What about those versed in scriptures and holy books, &lt;br&gt;
Are they the ones who find peace and experience bliss?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Efforts to Become Happy and Joyful</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/wiaposts/efforts-to-become-happy-and-joyful/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Nov 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/wiaposts/efforts-to-become-happy-and-joyful/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;../../assets/images/wiapost/5202-Efforts-To-Become-Happy-And-Joyful.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Efforts to Become Happy and Joyful&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Efforts to Become Happy and Joyful 
    &lt;div id=&#34;efforts-to-become-happy-and-joyful&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#efforts-to-become-happy-and-joyful&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We work hard to learn and earn.  &lt;br&gt;
This learning and earning helps us buying comfort in life&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We think comfortable things makes us happy  &lt;br&gt;
We forget there is very weak relationship between  &lt;br&gt;
Having comfortable things around and being happy&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;No matter how much we read and learn  &lt;br&gt;
No matter how we have and earn  &lt;br&gt;
Happiness come from understanding life  &lt;br&gt;
And joy comes from happiness.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>The Way Of Happiness</title>
